2017-03-29 Salvatore Iovene <salvatore.iovene@intel.com>
	* Release: 0.13.0-alpha
	* Monaco editor scrollbars are now thinner and less cluttered
	* The UI of various buttons is now more uniform
	* Dependency status is monitored via David-DM
	* We are now on top of Angular 4, and many other dependencies have been
	upgraded
	* Tab titles are not uppercase anymore
	* The Files and Examples sidebar elements are now their own Angular
	components
	* The GitHub modal is now a sidebar component
	* The separators between panes are now thinner

